Re: You only have to become stronger than your opponent
by Hyperworm » Thu 02.11.2010 6:44 pm （世界一最強の人になる必要はない。）相手より強くなれ（れ）ばそれでいい。I keep thinking you might be able to do something with さえ (相手より強くさえなれば...??) but it's not quite sounding natural for me...(I don't think you need なくてはいけない here. The core structure of the sentence isn't "You must become stronger than ...", it's "It's enough just to become stronger than ...".)
fun translation snippets | need something translated?BTC@1KMZXgoWiDshQis5Z7feCx8jaiP4QAB2ks
