Re: You only have to become stronger than your opponent
by Stefan » Mon 02.15.2010 2:54 am これがいかがであります？　ひとたびMANGAJINで読みました。相手を知れば、百戦あやうかならずopponent (obj) if know, 100 battles(usually just translated as many battles) safeknow your opponent and be safe though many battles. Hope I helped even a little. Stefan
